    (45, "Maillot lapinou", "Holiday Bunny", "Permet de modifier l'apparence d'EVE.", "Changes the appearance of EVE.", "Le tout dernier modèle de la collection estivale de Tetrastar C&T: le maillot de bain lapinou. L'immense majorité des consommateurs n'ont pas compris pourquoi ce nom avait été choisi, car les oreilles ne sont pas visibles de face.", "Introducing Tetrastar C&T's latest addition to their holiday collection: the bunny swimwear. Initially, customers were puzzled as to why it earned its name, considering the ears aren't visible from the front.", "Où la trouver ?", "Where to find it ?", "Dans la boutique Tetrastar C&T", "Unknown", "/images/nano_suits/unavailable.webp", "/icons/star_fill_blue.webp", 1),
